July 28, 2017 11:25 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Vertex One Asset Management Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Vertex One Asset Management Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals including personal holding companies, RRSPs, RRIFs, and family trusts. The firm manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It also manages hedge fund for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom up stock picking approach to make its investments. Vertex One Asset Management was founded in 1997 and is based in Vancouver, British Columbia.


Suite 32001021 West Hastings StreetVancouver, BC V6E 0C3CanadaFounded in 1997



Phone: 604-681-5787

Fax: 604-681-5146

www.vertexone.com







