We are an independent investment firm that seeks to offer investors a different
                approach to fund management, one based on capital preservation in both good and
                bad markets.
Through seven funds we offer investors a full spectrum of risk and return profiles,
                actively managed by asset class and strategy exposure.
Vertex employees are collectively the largest investors across its funds.



